      {
        "title": "Illusionist",
        "excerpt": "Powers          Name     Tier     Type     Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Color Spray                  Novice                                                                                                             Illusory Disguise                  Novice                                                                                                             Illusory Object                  Novice                                                                                                             Invisibility                  Novice                                                                                                             Phantom Pain                  Novice                                                                                                             Illusory Scene                  Veteran                                                                                     Phantasmal Killer                  Veteran                                                                                                             Shadow Siphon                  Veteran                                                                                                             Project Image                  Master                                                                                                             Weird                  Epic                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Tier Bonuses                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             Color Spray                              Novice                                       Incapacitation                    Spell                    Visual                                                      Cost           1 Mana                    Area           15-foot cone                    Save           Will                    Duration           1 or more rounds                                  Swirling colors affect viewers based on their Will saves.                                   Critical Success           The creature is unaffected                             Success           The creature is dazzled for 1 round                             Failure           The creature is stunned 1, blinded for 1 round, and dazzled for 1 minute                             Critical Failure           The creature is stunned for 1 round and blinded for 1 minute                                               Illusory Disguise                              Novice                                       Spell                    Visual                                                      Cost           1 Mana                    Duration           1 hour                                  You create an illusion that causes you to appear as another creature of the same body shape, and with roughly similar height and weight as yourself. The disguise is typically good enough to hide your identity, but not to impersonate a specific individual. The spell doesn’t change your voice, scent, or mannerisms. You can change the appearance of your clothing and worn items, but held items are unaffected, and any worn item you remove returns to its true appearance.      Heightened (total 2 Mana)   The spell also disguises your voice and scent, and it gains the Auditory trait   Heightened (total 3 Mana)   You can appear as any creature of the same size, even a specific individual as long as you’ve seen them before   Heightened (total 6 Mana)   You can target up to 10 creatures within 30 feet                                  Illusory Object                              Novice                                       Visual                    Spell                                                      Cost           1 Mana                    Range           500 feet                    Area           20-foot burst                    Duration           10 minutes                                  You create an illusory visual image of a stationary object. The entire image must fit within the spell’s area. The object appears to animate naturally, but it doesn’t make sounds or generate smells. Any creature that touches the image or uses the Seek action to examine it can attempt to disbelieve your illusion.      Heightened (total 2 Mana)   Your image makes appropriate sounds, generates normal smells, and feels right to the touch. The spell gains the Auditory trait. The duration increases to 1 hour.   Heightened (total 5 Mana)   The duration is unlimited.                                  Invisibility                              Novice                                       Spell                                                      Cost           2 Mana                    Range           Touch                    Duration           10 minutes                                  Cloaked in illusion, the target becomes invisible. This makes it hidden from all creatures that rely on sight. If the target uses a hostile action, the spell ends after that action is completed.      Heightened (total 4 Mana)   The spell lasts 1 minute, but it doesn’t end if the target uses a hostile action                                  Phantom Pain                              Novice                                       Mental                    Spell                                                      Cost           1 Mana                    Range           30 feet                    Save           Will                    Duration           1 minute                                  Illusory pain wracks the target, dealing 2d4 mental damage and 1d4 persistent mental damage. The target must attempt a Will save.                                   Critical Success           The target is unaffected                             Success           The target takes full initial damage but no persistent damage, and the spell ends immediately                             Failure           The target takes full initial and persistent damage, and the target is sickened 1                             Critical Failure           As failure, but the target is sickened 2                                               Illusory Scene              Veteran                                             Prerequisites           Illusory Object                                  Your Illusory Object power can form a scene that includes up to 10 moving creatures or objects. You can have each part of the scene follow a repeating program up to 1 minute long. A creature that interacts with one part of your image only disbelieves that portion.                                  Phantasmal Killer                              Veteran                                       Death                    Emotion                    Fear                    Mental                    Spell                                                      Cost           4 Mana                    Range           120 feet                    Save           Will                                  You create a phantasmal image of the most fearsome creature imaginable to the target. Only the spell’s target can see the killer, though you can see the vague shape of the illusion as it races forth to attack. The effect of the killer is based on the outcome of the target’s Will save.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The damage increases by 1d6 on a success, by 2d6 on a failure, and by 3d6 on a critical failure                                   Critical Success           The target is unaffected                             Success           The target takes 4d6 mental damage and is frightened 1                             Failure           The target takes 8d6 mental damage and is frightened 2                             Critical Failure           The target is so afraid it might die. It must attempt a Fortitude save (with the Incapacitation trait); if the target fails, it dies. On a successful Fortitude save, the target takes 12d6 mental damage, is fleeing until the end of its next turn, and is frightened 4.                                               Shadow Siphon                              Veteran                                       Shadow                    Spell                                                      Cost           5 Mana                    Range           60 feet                    Trigger           A spell or magical effect within range deals damage                                  Exchanging material energy with shadows, you transform the triggering spell into a partially illusory version of itself. Any creatures that would be damaged by the spell instead take only half as much damage, but the spell otherwise works as normal.                                  Project Image                              Master                                       Mental                    Spell                                                      Cost           7 Mana                    Range           30 feet                    Duration           Sustained up to 1 minute                                  You project an illusory image of yourself. You must stay within range of the image, and if at any point you can’t see the image, the spell ends. Whenever you cast a spell, you can cause the spell effect to originate from either yourself or the image. Because the image is an illusion, it isn’t a creature and can’t benefit from spells. The image has the same AC and saves as you. If it is hit by an attack or fails a save, the spell ends.      Heightened (total 9 Mana)   The maximum duration you can Sustan the spell increases to 10 minutes                                  Weird              Epic                                             Prerequisites           Phantasmal Killer                                  When you spend at least 8 Mana on Phantasmal Killer, the spell targets any number of creatures within range.",
        "url": "/illusionist.html"
      }
      
